hn@puck.news</a></u>) because I am dying to talk to you. My phone was blowi=
ng up with friends not involved in the sports business who had <i>plenty </=
i>of colorful things to say about them.<br/><br/>The good news is that, ear=
lier this week, MLB commissioner <b>Rob</b> <b>Manfred</b> appeared to open=
 the door to having players wear their regular uniforms during the game, li=
ke the old days, telling reporters that he=E2=80=99s =E2=80=9Caware of the =
